DOC.brief_summary: International Observational E-Registry on the use of DILAPAN-S® osmotic dilator / DILASOFT® osmotic dilator for cervical ripening prior to labour induction.
DOC.brief_title: Dilapan-S/Dilasoft E-Registry in Induction of Labor
DOC.detailed_description: International Observational E-Registry to monitor current common clinical practice of use of Dilapan-S / Dilasoft for cervical ripening and following procedures of labour induction with the main focus on the duration of induced labor procedure .
DOC.criteria: Indication for induction of labor Unfavourable cervix Presence of overt genital tract infection
